snippet.textDisplay: YES!!! 👏🏼 The Animal Crossing Nintendo Switch!! Would you be willing, when it has been released, to share your village ID(‘s)?? We already preordered the games (so we both have the card) and the case will be sent or received(not sure which one, I preordered it) on March 20th too! I am so excited! Let me know (hoping you read this) if you are up to share your village ID(’s). Or to receive mine, so we can visit each other!
